<P>
I would like everyone to think about the reason why they joined the guild in
the first place, my reason was : having fun, and sharing knowledge.  Some
people would give another Seeker the robe off of their own back to help
another Seeker in need, whilst others keep you waiting for 4 hours and then
tell you they sold it to the highest bidder.
<P>
I can not, and will not tolerate this !
